name: TVM Tote Bag
description:
Introducing the Tresor Vintage Market All-Over Print Tote Bag, a versatile and stylish addition to your everyday look. This tote is designed to combine practicality with vintage elegance, making it the perfect accessory for your daily outings. Whether you're carrying your laptop, notebook, or other essentials, this bag can handle it all with ease.


Product Details

Material: 100% polyester

Fabric Weight: 6.64 oz./yd.² (225 g/m²), may vary by 5%

Bag Size: 15″ × 15″ (38.1 × 38.1 cm)

Capacity: 2.6 US gal (10 l)

Maximum Weight Limit: 44 lbs. (20 kg)

Handles: Dual handles made from 100% natural cotton bull denim, 11.8″ (30 cm) in length and 1″ (2.5 cm) in width

Design: Printed, cut, and hand-sewn by our in-house team

Certification: Fabric is OEKO-TEX 100 standard certified

Origin: Blank product components sourced from Israel

Features

Durability: The bag is sturdy and capable of carrying up to 44 lbs., making it perfect for heavy loads.

Comfort: Dual handles ensure easy carrying, crafted from natural cotton bull denim for added comfort.

Eco-Friendly: OEKO-TEX 100 standard certified fabric, ensuring it's free from harmful substances.


Benefits of On-Demand Manufacturing

This product is made especially for you as soon as you place an order, which helps reduce overproduction and promotes sustainable, thoughtful purchasing decisions. Thank you for supporting eco-friendly craftsmanship!


Traceability

Knitting: China

Dyeing: China

Manufacturing: Latvia

Note: This item releases plastic microfibers into the environment during washing. Contains 0% recycled polyester and 0% dangerous substances.


Embrace Style and Functionality

Upgrade your accessory collection with the Tresor Vintage Market All-Over Print Tote Bag. Its unique design and high-quality materials make it a bestseller in our store. Order now and carry your essentials in style with this elegant and durable tote bag!
